OL,3,CTesco creates seedless hybrid fruit as
OL,4,CUK tastes change
OL,6,Fis launching a range of new hybrid
OL,7,Feasy-peelers, as UK shoppers tastes
OL,8,Fchange.
OL,10,FThe supermarket giant has been working
OL,11,Fwith Spanish and Moroccan growers on
OL,12,Fproducing so-called mandarin hybrids
OL,13,Fwhich have fewer pips.
OL,15,FGrowers in the two countries have been
OL,16,Freducing their production of satsumas
OL,17,Fbecause the European market
OL,18,Ftraditionally prefers seeded
OL,19,Fclementines.
