OL,3,CTesco creates seedless hybrid fruit as
OL,4,CUK tastes change
OL,6,FBut, according to Tesco, Brits are
OL,7,Fbigger fans of satsumas, which are
OL,8,Funseeded.
OL,10,FIn response, the superstore it is now
OL,11,Flaunching four varieties of hybrid
OL,12,Fmandarin ` Meiravit, Havva, Orit and
OL,13,FSigal ` which have fewer pips, are
OL,14,Fless susceptible to early season
OL,15,Fgreening and have a longer shelf life,
OL,16,Fas well as having a vibrant colour and
OL,17,Fbeing more aromatic.
