OL,3,CTesco creates seedless hybrid fruit as
OL,4,CUK tastes change
OL,6,FThe popularity of mandarin hybrids is
OL,7,Fgrowing each year in the UK, and last
OL,8,Fyear Tesco shoppers bought roughly
OL,9,Ftwice as many as they did in 2017, the
OL,10,Fsupermarket said.
OL,12,FThe hybrids could take over from
OL,13,Fclementines completely in the next
OL,14,Fdecade, it added.
OL,16,FSupplier AMT Fresh is one of the UK's
OL,17,Fbiggest importers of citrus fruit and
OL,18,Fhas been working with Tesco.
