OL,3,CTesco creates seedless hybrid fruit as
OL,4,CUK tastes change
OL,6,F"A hybrid is a cross between two
OL,7,Fvarieties, and in this case that could
OL,8,Fbe other mandarins, clementines,
OL,9,Fsatsumas, oranges or even grapefruit,"
OL,10,FBennie Smidt, head of agronomy at AMT
OL,11,FFresh said.
OL,13,F"A cross means taking pollen from a
OL,14,Fcertain variety and pollinating a
OL,15,Fflower of a different variety. The
OL,16,Fresulting seeds within the fruits are
OL,17,Fthe hybrids, which will need to be
OL,18,Fgrown, selected, screened and
OL,19,Fpropagated if successful."
