OL,6,FHe said that it could "take up to 20
OL,7,Fyears before it reaches the market in
OL,8,Fcommercial volumes".
OL,10,FThe reduced number of satsumas being
OL,11,Fproduced had led to some changes in UK
OL,12,Ftastes towards clementines, Mr Smidt
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,F"As a result of their stronger taste,
OL,16,Fconsumer preference switched over from
OL,17,Fsatsumas ` when they were available `
OL,18,Fto clementines.
OL,20,F"But there was still the matter of
OL,21,Fseeds.
